ing: 3 pounds potatoes - peeled, boiled and diced
2 (14.5 ounce) cans peeled and diced tomatoes
2 (1 ounce) packages dry onion soup mix
des: "This is a veggie-soup-to-die-for! Our weekends are so busy, Friday night is soup night, and this is it! Wonderful with crackers or some herbed rolls. This may also be made with pasta, leaving out the potatoes. Just add 2 cups uncooked macaroni or soup ring pasta in the last 10-15 minutes of cook time. Stir occasionally to keep separate."
ins:
Combine frozen vegetables, potatoes, onion, celery, tomatoes, tomato sauce, water, and onion soup mix, mix well. Cover and cook over medium low heat, stirring occasionally, for 2-3 hours.
Serve hot with cold evaporated milk, if desired.
